{"tid":2462790,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「千年一遇美少女」橋本環奈自爆童年照","createTime":"2021-03-26T08:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T08:26:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff02e382299ce00aac545c1f88f75b591d6ba5c","tid":2462790,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T08:23:03.000Z","msg":"成日都話「女大十八變」，呢句說話確實無錯嘅，不過總有啲人例外，係由靚變成更靚，從細靚到大。被譽為「千年一遇美少女」嘅橋本環奈，最近就Twitter晒出多張童年照，可愛模樣引起粉絲大讚。<br />\n<br />\n橋本環奈表示最近好似少咗喺Twiiter上講私事，所以放幾張童年照畀大家睇，由手抱BB到識行識走嘅橋本環奈從此曝光，一日之間就有17萬個LIKE，有網民更留言Post返佢仲係學生妹嗰陣嘅相。<br />\n<br />\n今次唔係橋本環奈第一次Post童年照，曾經就喺「いい双子の日」Post過雙胞胎哥哥嘅相。<br />\n<br />\n橋本環奈最近忙於拍新劇「インフルエンス」，更話即使做左N次核酸測試都怕自己中肺炎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExS1HTMUcAMWmPd?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FExS1HTMUcAMWmPd%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=1b07d5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExS1HTPVIAA_0OI?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FExS1HTPVIAA_0OI%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=8fbfb501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExS1HTPVoAIg3zc?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FExS1HTPVoAIg3zc%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=1af869bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExS1HTNUcAM8kuo?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FExS1HTNUcAM8kuo%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=5fad2c37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bbe4e98861417b54675f9dd65159f6c740b93d0","tid":2462790,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"橋本仲有無食避孕食到好肥?"}]}